{
 "cells": [
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "## Representations of su(4)\n\nConstructs finite-dimensional irreps of $\\mathfrak{gl}(4)$ (equivalently $\\mathfrak{su}(4)$ irreps, realized as $\\mathfrak{gl}(4)$-modules) via Gelfand-Tsetlin patterns. `ps[rep]` enumerates the GT basis for highest weight `rep`, `dim[rep]` is the representation dimension, and `J0`/`Jp`/`Jm`/`JJ` give the matrix elements of the Cartan and raising/lowering generators $J_{kk}$, $J_{k,k+1}$, $J_{k+1,k}$ in this basis, with general $J_{kl}$ obtained by commutators.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ps[rep_] := \n  ps[rep] = \n   Block[{res = (Prepend[rep, #] & /@ (Tuples[\n          Table[Range[rep[[1, i + 1]], rep[[1, i]]], {i, 1, \n            Length[rep[[1]]] - 1}]]))}, \n    If[Length[res[[1, 1]]] == 1, Reverse@Sort@res, \n     Reverse@Sort@Flatten[ps /@ res, 1]]];\ndim[rep_] := dim[rep] = Length[ps[{rep}]];\nJ0[k_][pat_] := \n  J0[k][pat] = \n   Sum[pat[[k, i]], {i, 1, k}] - Sum[pat[[k - 1, i]], {i, 1, k - 1}];\nJp[k_][pat_] := \n  Jp[k][pat] = -Sum[\n     Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k + 1, j]] + j, {j, \n         Range[k + 1]}]/\n       Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j, \n         Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[\n       ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] + 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJm[k_][pat_] := \n  Jm[k][pat] = \n   Sum[Product[\n       pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k - 1, j]] + j, {j, Range[k - 1]}]/\n      Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j, \n        Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[\n      ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] - 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJJ[k_, l_, rep_] := \n  JJ[k, l, rep] = \n   Which[k == l, DiagonalMatrix[J0[k] /@ ps[{rep}]], l == k + 1, \n    Transpose[\n     Table[Coefficient[Jp[k][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@ \n       ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l == k - 1, \n    Transpose[\n     Table[Coefficient[Jm[l][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@ \n       ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l > k + 1, \n    JJ[k, k + 1, rep] . JJ[k + 1, l, rep] - \n     JJ[k + 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k + 1, rep], l < k - 1, \n    JJ[k, k - 1, rep] . JJ[k - 1, l, rep] - \n     JJ[k - 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k - 1, rep]];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "Sanity check: evaluates the diagonal (Cartan) generator $J_{1,1}$ on the $\\mathfrak{su}(4)$ representation with highest weight $(2,1,0)$, displayed as a matrix in the Gelfand-Tsetlin basis.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "JJ[1,1,{2,1,0}] // MatrixForm",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"225514\" data-output-id=\"0\" data-out-n=\"13\" data-sub-idx=\"0\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"2\" data-sub-start=\"0\" data-sub-end=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[13]//MatrixForm=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrhc9o9s-1atw5pt\" data-page-width-em=\"80\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:9.6001em;vertical-align:-4.5501em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:5.0499em;\"><span style=\"top:-7.0499em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:11.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:9.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"9.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 9600\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,6084c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7,-112.5,-882c-2,-104,-3,-167,-3,-189\nl0,-6092c0,-162.7,5.7,-314,17,-454c20.7,-272,63.7,-513,129,-723c65.3,\n-210,155.3,-396.3,270,-559c6.7,-9.3,10,-15.3,10,-18z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><spa